sources.title: Pungo: A Witch's Tale | Full Movie | Fantasy Horror
sources.description:
Pungo: A Witch's Tale - A burned-out ex-Navy SEAL and an emotionally-damaged firefighter work together as handymen in Tidewater Virginia. Things turn surreal when a simple renovation job becomes a journey to another world to rescue their client from a trans-dimensional witch bent on revenge in this imaginative take on Grace Sherwood-the Witch of Pungo.
2020.  Stars: Mark Hyde, Matthew Sharpe, Cathryn Benson
